data.description: Welcome to the Reserve at the Terrace in the neighborhood of Westover Hills, San Antonio. This stunning home, boasting almost 2800 square feet of luxurious living space, is a perfect blend of modern comfort and elegance. With 4 bedrooms and 3 and a half baths, this property offers ample space for anyone that is seeking a spacious retreat.    Step inside and be captivated by the inviting open floor plan, designed to enhance the experience of entertaining. The seamless flow between the living area, dining space, and kitchen allows for easy interaction with guests while hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories.    Situated on almost a third of an acre, the backyard is nothing short of a private oasis. You'll find yourself surrounded by lush greenery, providing a sense of tranquility and seclusion. Whether it's a weekend barbecue or a serene evening under the stars, this expansive backyard is sure to become your favorite outdoor haven.    As you ascend the stairs, you'll be delighted to discover a spacious game room, providing endless possibilities for recreation and relaxation. Additionally, the home offers a dedicated office space and formal dining room on the lower level, catering to your professional and social needs.    One of the many advantages of this home is its prime location within walking distance to the local high school providing both convenience and peace of mind. Moreover, being nestled within a gated community ensures an added layer of security and exclusivity for you and your loved ones.    In summary, this home in the Reserve at the Terrace caters to every aspect of comfortable and stylish living. Schedule your showing today so you don't miss the opportunity to call this house your own!
